Stylus is a code formatter for Lua, it is a tool that helps you to format your code in a way that it is easy to read and understand. With this program you can make your code look neat and organized, this way it will be much easier to find and fix any mistakes. The program works by taking your code and rearranging it in a way that makes it easy to read, it also adds indentation and spacing to help you see the structure of your code. Additionally, Stylus also has a feature that allows you to customize your code formatting settings, so you can make your code look exactly the way you want it to. This is a great tool for programmers of all skill levels, whether you are a beginner or an experienced developer. 